  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a deck of heroes from Greek mythology </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of the five Deities, each one with their own power </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain new spells, enhancements, and hero cards to conquer more realms </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classical art by world-renowned painters like John Waterhouse and Frederic Leighton </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete on the Online Leaderboard </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Power of the Gods</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a Greek Deity and build a deck of heroes, spells, and enhancements to compete with others on the Global Leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/ba99bd9d429d6d60ba1a1749ef96b69f.poster.avif?t=1773603968\" width=598 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/ba99bd9d429d6d60ba1a1749ef96b69f.webm?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/ba99bd9d429d6d60ba1a1749ef96b69f.mp4?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strategy and Synergy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hone your deck-building skills to conquer as many realms as possible. Your starting deck can be modified in tons of ways to create interesting builds synergizing with each of the five deities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/147cc14abeed783d718c35f06e6af3dc.poster.avif?t=1773603968\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/147cc14abeed783d718c35f06e6af3dc.webm?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/147cc14abeed783d718c35f06e6af3dc.mp4?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ascend Divinity</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the Blind Poet between conquered realms to modify your deck with new cards. Defeat rival Deities who dare summon themselves to the board, and claim their power to ascend Olympus!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/f8a1dc5f9834319717ea8e93be8d1ded.poster.avif?t=1773603968\" width=598 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/f8a1dc5f9834319717ea8e93be8d1ded.webm?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/f8a1dc5f9834319717ea8e93be8d1ded.mp4?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Life and Legacy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anticipate your enemies and manage your token economy, watch each hero's golden lotus closely— when the final petal falls, the hero will perish. Yet their legacy inspires the strength of those who will come after.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a deck of heroes from Greek mythology </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of the five Deities, each one with their own power </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain new spells, enhancements, and hero cards to conquer more realms </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classical art by world-renowned painters like John Waterhouse and Frederic Leighton </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete on the Online Leaderboard </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Power of the Gods</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a Greek Deity and build a deck of heroes, spells, and enhancements to compete with others on the Global Leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/ba99bd9d429d6d60ba1a1749ef96b69f.poster.avif?t=1773603968\" width=598 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/ba99bd9d429d6d60ba1a1749ef96b69f.webm?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/ba99bd9d429d6d60ba1a1749ef96b69f.mp4?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strategy and Synergy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hone your deck-building skills to conquer as many realms as possible. Your starting deck can be modified in tons of ways to create interesting builds synergizing with each of the five deities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/147cc14abeed783d718c35f06e6af3dc.poster.avif?t=1773603968\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/147cc14abeed783d718c35f06e6af3dc.webm?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/147cc14abeed783d718c35f06e6af3dc.mp4?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ascend Divinity</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the Blind Poet between conquered realms to modify your deck with new cards. Defeat rival Deities who dare summon themselves to the board, and claim their power to ascend Olympus!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/f8a1dc5f9834319717ea8e93be8d1ded.poster.avif?t=1773603968\" width=598 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/f8a1dc5f9834319717ea8e93be8d1ded.webm?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/f8a1dc5f9834319717ea8e93be8d1ded.mp4?t=1773603968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Life and Legacy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anticipate your enemies and manage your token economy, watch each hero's golden lotus closely— when the final petal falls, the hero will perish. Yet their legacy inspires the strength of those who will come after.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
